There are more than 300 different kinds of crops grown in Mexico. Maize is a very important crop for Mexicans, we would like to know which states have the largest production.

mex %>% select(Nomcultivo, Idcultivo, Volumenproduccion) %>%  group_by(Nomcultivo) %>% summarise(total=sum(Volumenproduccion)) %>% arrange(desc(total))

Maize
